{"type":"text","timestamp":1778698266647,"sessionID":"ses_1dd53290dffeoniMMBnoeZ6EmF","part":{"id":"prt_e22ad9dfb0016lIYlJ7H24juhD","messageID":"msg_e22ad056a001ikUJdbTNoYjM60","sessionID":"ses_1dd53290dffeoniMMBnoeZ6EmF","type":"text","text":"Prior micro-opt attempts show the only large win was a narrow ALU datapath simplification; most added state, prediction, reset trimming, and metadata cleanup regressed or broke. I’m choosing another narrow behavior-preserving micro-opt: remove the impossible EX/MEM load-forward case so the forwarding priority path only treats values actually available in EX/MEM as bypassable.","time":{"start":1778698264059,"end":1778698266646},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_02c667ca10094235016a04c817f2fc819a9caac072ad41c1f7","phase":"commentary"}}}}
