e no longer needs to route the LUI immediate through its output mux.\"\n+  - file: rtl/decoder.sv\n+    description: \"Keep LUI legal with ctrl.is_lui/reg_write/alu_src set, but assign a simple non-special ALU op because EX now handles the LUI result directly.\"\n","additions":19,"deletions":0}],"diagnostics":{},"truncated":false},"title":"Success. Updated the following files:\nA cores/bench/experiments/hypotheses/hyp-20260513-001-r14s0.yaml","time":{"start":1778701993171,"end":1778701993178}},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"fc_076bf61898336e71016a04d693bd8c81998aed2232850fa3ac"}},"id":"prt_e22e63181001dpB3ctLOjDuOvJ","sessionID":"ses_1dd1aebf5ffeRwYw5wzZrFDViu","messageID":"msg_e22e6246c0016ILhkda4l4u2g6"}}
