{"type":"text","timestamp":1778679173676,"sessionID":"ses_1de762601ffeqQ4Q0OHTLoh5cL","part":{"id":"prt_e218a492900153PM6b7scHif0T","messageID":"msg_e218a03f5001fJqDnlpgqIsTR4","sessionID":"ses_1de762601ffeqQ4Q0OHTLoh5cL","type":"text","text":"Prior structural attempt moved M ops out of the main ALU and regressed because added blocking stalls outweighed Fmax gains. I’m choosing a structural IPC improvement instead: bypass ready load data directly from MEM to the dependent EX instruction to remove the classic load-use bubble when the data bus is ready.","time":{"start":1778679171369,"end":1778679173674},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_061cf088343a5fd5016a047d83387c819ab5264297cd8a97a9","phase":"commentary"}}}}
