{"type":"text","timestamp":1778680254023,"sessionID":"ses_1de65a0efffethTDFbccQ3rAe5","part":{"id":"prt_e219acc1d001m8Vc0w7GXxGefV","messageID":"msg_e219a9f1c002s5yV5B196lgjdH","sessionID":"ses_1de65a0efffethTDFbccQ3rAe5","type":"text","text":"Prior predictor attempts both pushed prediction through ID decode and lost Fmax or metadata correctness. I’m going to target the lesson directly with a tiny fetch-PC-indexed BTB so prediction does not depend on the `imem_data -> decode -> immediate add -> PC` path.","time":{"start":1778680253469,"end":1778680254022},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_07c3f98b807e426e016a0481bd5ea08199a811338f561660d2","phase":"commentary"}}}}
