{"type":"text","timestamp":1778684195863,"sessionID":"ses_1de299b11ffeD547owEKVaQwUa","part":{"id":"prt_e21d6f036001NSndhcrYIqUdAl","messageID":"msg_e21d69a31001VZiudlHSN7u4TE","sessionID":"ses_1de299b11ffeD547owEKVaQwUa","type":"text","text":"The prior predictor attempts failed on decode-time conditional prediction critical paths and BTB formal complexity. I’m going to write a narrower predictor hypothesis: early static prediction only for unconditional `JAL`, with explicit predicted-next-PC metadata so EX does not re-flush correctly predicted jumps.","time":{"start":1778684194870,"end":1778684195861},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_0158b68429a74013016a049122c098819a858a8aec7aca3590","phase":"commentary"}}}}
