{"type":"text","timestamp":1778686804975,"sessionID":"ses_1de018b45ffekdfZ3EdDJoPFDU","part":{"id":"prt_e21fec160001AV5LaaGgLZTfZY","messageID":"msg_e21fe9f7c001IUU1RaSRWdVyCi","sessionID":"ses_1de018b45ffekdfZ3EdDJoPFDU","type":"text","text":"The prior predictor attempts failed mainly by putting target generation on the imem/decode critical path or by adding mutable BTB state that made formal hard. I’m going to propose a narrower predictor that avoids changing fetch PC timing: an EX-stage one-bit last-outcome bypass for conditional branches to suppress redundant redirects only when the fall-through/taken decision repeats at the same PC.","time":{"start":1778686804320,"end":1778686804973},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_0689c50c9fb23e21016a049b5430f08198834c80eda424a5a3","phase":"commentary"}}}}
