{"type":"text","timestamp":1778695054190,"sessionID":"ses_1dd83eecfffeVt6cbYivQFYBs6","part":{"id":"prt_e227ca2d6001mznbVjrr6fkAy3","messageID":"msg_e227c4ab9001frIPk5HdmsEUF8","sessionID":"ses_1dd83eecfffeVt6cbYivQFYBs6","type":"text","text":"The predictor history is uniformly negative except the one-entry backward loop predictor, which was only a small regression. I’m going to avoid decode-time target generation and general BTBs, and propose a narrower registered fetch-side predictor for repeated unconditional `JAL` sites only.","time":{"start":1778695054038,"end":1778695054188},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_06592c19a1be0be0016a04bb8ded38819bb1d1fdb158504642","phase":"commentary"}}}}
